msgstr "Linked Discourses 45"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "sn45.155:0.2"
msgid "12. Balakaraṇīyavagga"
msgstr "12. Hard Work"

#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "sn45.155:0.3"
msgid "155. Ākāsasutta"
msgstr "155. The Sky"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pi" id="pts-vp-pi5.50"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "sn45.155:1.1"
msgid "“Seyyathāpi, bhikkhave, ākāse vividhā vātā vāyanti—"
msgstr "“Mendicants, various winds blow in the sky."

msgctxt "sn45.155:1.2"
msgid ""
"puratthimāpi vātā vāyanti, pacchimāpi vātā vāyanti, uttarāpi vātā vāyanti, "
"dakkhiṇāpi vātā vāyanti, sarajāpi vātā vāyanti, arajāpi vātā vāyanti, sītāpi "
"vātā vāyanti, uṇhāpi vātā vāyanti, parittāpi vātā vāyanti, adhimattāpi vātā "
"vāyanti;"
msgstr ""
"Winds blow from the east, the west, the north, and the south. There are "
"winds that are dusty and dustless, cool and warm, weak and strong."

msgctxt "sn45.155:1.3"
msgid ""
"evameva kho, bhikkhave, bhikkhuno ariyaṃ aṭṭhaṅgikaṃ maggaṃ bhāvayato ariyaṃ "
"aṭṭhaṅgikaṃ maggaṃ bahulīkaroto cattāropi satipaṭṭhānā bhāvanāpāripūriṃ "
"gacchanti, cattāropi sammappadhānā bhāvanāpāripūriṃ gacchanti, cattāropi "
"iddhipādā bhāvanāpāripūriṃ gacchanti, pañcapi indriyāni bhāvanāpāripūriṃ "
"gacchanti, pañcapi balāni bhāvanāpāripūriṃ gacchanti, sattapi bojjhaṅgā "
"bhāvanāpāripūriṃ gacchanti."
msgstr ""
"In the same way, when the noble eightfold path is developed and cultivated "
"the following are developed to perfection: the four kinds of mindfulness "
"meditation, the four right efforts, the four bases of psychic power, the "
"five faculties, the five powers, and the seven awakening factors."

msgctxt "sn45.155:1.4"
msgid ""
"Kathañca, bhikkhave, bhikkhuno ariyaṃ aṭṭhaṅgikaṃ maggaṃ bhāvayato ariyaṃ "
"aṭṭhaṅgikaṃ maggaṃ bahulīkaroto cattāropi satipaṭṭhānā bhāvanāpāripūriṃ "
"gacchanti, cattāropi sammappadhānā bhāvanāpāripūriṃ gacchanti, cattāropi "
"iddhipādā bhāvanāpāripūriṃ gacchanti, pañcapi indriyāni bhāvanāpāripūriṃ "
"gacchanti, pañcapi balāni bhāvanāpāripūriṃ gacchanti, sattapi bojjhaṅgā "
"bhāvanāpāripūriṃ gacchanti?"
msgstr "And how are they developed to perfection?"

msgctxt "sn45.155:1.5"
msgid ""
"Idha, bhikkhave, bhikkhu sammādiṭṭhiṃ bhāveti … pe … sammāsamādhiṃ bhāveti "
"vivekanissitaṃ virāganissitaṃ nirodhanissitaṃ vossaggapariṇāmiṃ …"
msgstr ""
"It’s when a mendicant develops right view, right thought, right speech, "
"right action, right livelihood, right effort, right mindfulness, and right "
"immersion, which rely on seclusion, fading away, and cessation, and ripen as "
"letting go."

msgctxt "sn45.155:1.6"
msgid ""
"evaṃ kho, bhikkhave, bhikkhuno ariyaṃ aṭṭhaṅgikaṃ maggaṃ bhāvayato ariyaṃ "
"aṭṭhaṅgikaṃ maggaṃ bahulīkaroto cattāropi satipaṭṭhānā bhāvanāpāripūriṃ "
"gacchanti, cattāropi sammappadhānā bhāvanāpāripūriṃ gacchanti, cattāropi "
"iddhipādā bhāvanāpāripūriṃ gacchanti, pañcapi indriyāni bhāvanāpāripūriṃ "
"gacchanti, pañcapi balāni bhāvanāpāripūriṃ gacchanti, sattapi bojjhaṅgā "
"bhāvanāpāripūriṃ gacchantī”ti."
msgstr "That’s how they’re developed to perfection.”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn45.155:1.7"
msgid "Sattamaṃ."
msgstr ""
